detail_desc: Fully lined, waist-high bikini bottoms in fast-drying functional fabric with medium coverage at the back.
Fully lined sports swimsuit with a high-cut top and visible zip with a long tab at the back. Mesh back section, high-cut legs and medium coverage at the back.
Lined bikini top with a mesh racer back and wide elastic hem.
Lined bikini top with a mesh racer back and wide elastic hem.
Gently tailored, double-breasted jacket in a textured weave containing some wool with notch lapels, welt front pockets and decorative buttons at the cuffs. Lined.
Long-sleeved swimsuit in fast-drying functional fabric with a small stand-up collar, a zip at the top with a long tab, and a lined gusset. Lined at the front.
Long-sleeved swimsuit in fast-drying functional fabric with a small stand-up collar, a zip at the top with a long tab, and a lined gusset. Lined at the front.
Long-sleeved dress in soft jersey with a reversible sequin motif on the front (size 2-4Y with normal sequins), seam at the waist and flared skirt.
Trousers in soft velvet with a high waist, concealed zip in one side, side pockets and wide legs.

Bikini top in fast-drying functional fabric. Narrow cut at the top and a lined front with removable inserts that shape the bust and provide good support. Asymmetric seam under the bust, a wide elastic trim at the hem and mesh racer back with a chunky zip.

Bikini top in fast-drying functional fabric. Narrow cut at the top and a lined front with removable inserts that shape the bust and provide good support. Asymmetric seam under the bust, a wide elastic trim at the hem and mesh racer back with a chunky zip.
Nylon windbreaker with a stand-up collar, drawstring hood and zip down the front. Side pockets with a taped zip, and narrow elastication at the cuffs and hem. Mesh lining.
Nylon windbreaker with a stand-up collar, drawstring hood and zip down the front. Side pockets with a taped zip, and narrow elastication at the cuffs and hem. Mesh lining.
Nylon windbreaker with a stand-up collar, drawstring hood and zip down the front. Side pockets with a taped zip, and narrow elastication at the cuffs and hem. Mesh lining.

Lightweight puffer jacket in woven fabric with a hood and discreet zip down the front with a chin guard. Pockets in the side seams with a concealed zip, and narrow elastication at the cuffs and hem. Unlined.

Fully lined sports bra in ribbed, fast-drying functional fabric with removable inserts, adjustable shoulder straps that split into three at the back, and an elasticated hem. Light support.
Fitted jacket in woven fabric with a shawl collar, concealed hook-and-eye fastening, long sleeves and jetted front pockets. Lined.
Fitted jacket in woven fabric with a shawl collar, concealed hook-and-eye fastening, long sleeves and jetted front pockets. Lined.
High-waisted leggings in glossy jersey with covered elastication at the waist.
High-waisted leggings in glossy jersey with covered elastication at the waist.
High-waisted leggings in glossy jersey with covered elastication at the waist.
Thin Alice band in metal with pearly beads.

Ankle-length sports tights in fast-drying functional fabric with a high, V-shaped waist with wide, gathered elastication. The tights are designed with the minimum number of seams for a more comfortable fit and increased mobility. The polyamide content of the tights is partly recycled.

Patterned fancy dress costume with embroidered details and felt appliqués. Sleeveless top in solid colour jersey with a concealed hook and loop fastening at the back and long legs. Padded section at the front in the shape of a dinosaur with handles at the top that have a hook and loop fastening. Detachable, padded tail at the back.
Soft pile slippers with glittery embroidery and appliqués on the front. Pile linings and insoles and soles with anti-slip protectors.
Bracelets in fabric and metal with decorative shells.
Negligee in lace with underwired, padded cups for a larger bust and fuller cleavage. Narrow, adjustable shoulder straps and an opening and hook-and-eye fastening at the back.
Soft, non-wired bra in lace with removable inserts that shape the bust and provide good support. Adjustable shoulder straps, and a metal fastening at the front.
